product_name: Handcrafted Banana Fiber Spacious Sling Bag For Women To Suit Your Style
description:
JUTE BAGS

Introducing our stunning Jute Bags, a fusion of contemporary style and eco-conscious fashion. This handcrafted bag seamlessly combines the earthy charm of jute with bold and vibrant colours, creating a standout accessory that adds a touch of sophistication to your ensemble.

Key Features:

Handcrafted Artistry: Each bag is meticulously handcrafted by skilled artisans, ensuring attention to detail and the highest quality. The craftsmanship adds an element of uniqueness to each piece, making your bag a one-of-a-kind fashion statement.
Practical and Compact: The jute bag is designed with practicality in mind. It offers enough space to carry your essentials, such as a wallet, phone, keys, makeup, books, and laptop while remaining compact and easy to carry.
Versatile Use: Whether you’re heading to a casual outing, a shopping spree, or a day at the office, the Jute bag complements your style and adds a touch of elegance to any occasion.
Conscious Fashion Choice: By owning this jute purse, you make a conscious choice to support sustainable fashion and promote eco-friendly practices, helping to protect our environment.
QUALITY WORTH EVERY PENNY

Eco-Friendly Material: Our Jute Bags are made from 100% natural jute fiber, a sustainable and biodegradable material that aligns with your eco-conscious values. By choosing these bags, you contribute to a greener and cleaner planet.
Chic Color Combination: The sophisticated pairing of different hues creates a visually striking contrast that complements a wide range of outfits, from casual to semi-formal. The bag becomes a statement piece that effortlessly elevates your style.
Secure Closure: The bag features a secure zipper closure, keeping your belongings safe and preventing anything from falling out.
specification:
Weight 250 g
Dimensions 20 × 6 × 18 cm
Color 
Cream Base

Material 
Polyester
